From dcf03122db2d9ab45635eb43f1b23eb62f60d4f3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jack Thomson <jackabt@amazon.com>
Date: Tue, 2 Jun 2026 16:03:24 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 92/94] KVM: x86: Advertise userfault async page faults

Advertise base userfault async page fault support separately from the
exitless eventfd fast path.

Enable the per-vCPU capability, document the KVM_ASYNC_PF ioctl, and add
a selftest for the exit-based ACCEPT/READY and autocomplete flows.
Keeping this commit limited to the non-exitless API lets
KVM_CAP_ASYNC_PF_USERFAULT describe a useful standalone feature.

Signed-off-by: Jack Thomson <jackabt@amazon.com>
